proving its validity.

135
00:06:44,125 --> 00:06:45,325
Great.

136
00:06:45,327 --> 00:06:48,595
Now, this may look
like a Tic Tac...

137
00:06:50,281 --> 00:06:55,051
...but it is really a powerful
medication specifically designed

138
00:06:55,053 --> 00:06:58,721
