like this.

203
00:10:18,422 --> 00:10:20,590
S'up?

204
00:10:29,076 --> 00:10:31,794
Step one: worms.

205
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:35,248
Ew!

206
00:10:36,216 --> 00:10:38,301
Okay, right there,
"ew" is one of the things

207
00:10:38,303 --> 00:10:40,920
